casebody.data:
Number 121 Madison Ave., Appellant, v. Osgood, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

May 12, 1892.) Action by Humber 121 Madison Avenue (a corporation) against John C. Osgood.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bischoff, JJ.

Ho opinion. Motion for reargument or leave to appeal to the court of appeals denied, with $10 costs. See 18 N. Y. Supp. 126.
